(firstQuint)Evaluation of Use of Brain Activity Monitoring Dynamics in ADHD.

 The study will be conducted in two arms (arm I and arm II).

 In arm I, participants diagnosed with ADD/ADHD.

 In arm II, healthy participants.

 The status of the participants will be evaluated with questionnaires computerized test and EEG characteristics will be collected for all study participants.

